<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="rest-v">rest <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rest/    美 /rest/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 休息：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>rest one’s brain / eyes 
让大脑/眼睛休息</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She never had a moment to rest. 
她从没得到过片刻休息。</p></div></div>